item.description:
Summer is rapidly winding down for everyone and before we know it there will be a blanket of that four letter white stuff covering the ground. So we'd like to get together this month and use this meeting time to share with everyone what we've done (photography or using any of the Adobe products). Bring items to share if you can otherwise you can use the time to explain what you've done.

In addition to this month's meeting, we are hoping to get a group together for an informal "photo walk". There is a tentative date of August 26th for the photo walk.

Hope to see you all on Thursday evening!
item.name: August Manchester Adobe User Group Meeting
